    <body>
        <div class="Example">
            <h6>Example: Using the grep template function</h6>
            <p>The following example selects the message of the context that has a <b class="Code">username</b> name-value pair with the <b class="Code">root</b> value, and returns the value of the <span class="Code">auth_method</span> name-value pair.</p><pre>$(grep ("${username}" == "root") ${auth_method})</pre>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>